# Project Overview

This project analyzes longitudinal PBMC single-cell RNA-seq data with matched BCR repertoire data.

## Study design

Samples are grouped into:

- Control
- Death
- Live

Time points include:

- Control
- T0
- T1
- T2
- T3

## Objectives

- define immune cell composition changes over time
- identify major and fine-grained immune cell states
- characterize B-cell differentiation states
- compare death vs live trajectories
- analyze BCR clonotype expansion, diversity, isotype usage, and SHM

## Data modalities

- 10X Genomics scRNA-seq
- BCR repertoire contig tables

## Main outputs

- integrated Seurat object
- annotated major and minor cell types
- composition plots
- DEG tables
- GSEA and GO enrichment results
- clonotype and isotype summaries
- SHM summary tables and plots
